OL,7,FIn response, Health Secretary Wes
OL,8,FStreeting told ITV News the concerns
OL,9,Fraised in our report give him
OL,10,F"sleepless nights" and he is looking
OL,11,Finto tightening "the supervision and
OL,12,Fcontrol" of some mental health
OL,13,Fpatients in the UK.
OL,15,FJane has shown ITV News dozens of
OL,16,Femails and letters she's sent to
OL,17,Fdoctors, mental health professionals
OL,18,Fand MPs asking for help.
