OL,7,FIn one message she wrote: "What are
OL,8,Fyou going to do, wait until he's
OL,9,Fkilled me?"
OL,11,FIn an email sent to a doctor,
OL,12,Ffollowing the attacks in Nottingham in
OL,13,FJune 2023, in which three people were
OL,14,Fkilled by schizophrenic Valdo
OL,15,FCalocane, Jane desperately pleads for
OL,16,Fmore support.
OL,18,F"Don't let him become another Valdo
OL,19,FCalocane, because I'm telling you,
OL,20,Fhe's another tragedy waiting to
OL,21,Fhappen. Please listen to me," it said.
