OL,7,FITV News was given permission to film
OL,8,Fwith an Assertive Outreach Team in
OL,9,FLeeds, where we joined a consultant
OL,10,Fpsychiatrist and nurse as they went
OL,11,Fout to treat patients with severe
OL,12,Fmental illness.
OL,14,FThe team provides long-term care for
OL,15,Fpeople who find it difficult to accept
OL,16,Fsupport from community mental health
OL,17,Fteams.
OL,19,FThey check patients are taking their
OL,20,Fmedication and can help with other
OL,21,Fissues like housing and employment.
