OL,7,F"We go to the patient, we don't expect
OL,8,Fthem to come to us," Consultant
OL,9,FPsychiatrist Dr Nuwan Dissanayaka told
OL,10,FITV News.
OL,12,F"People who are living with very
OL,13,Fsevere mental illness have a life that
OL,14,Fis hard for most of us to imagine.
OL,16,F"They might be very mistrustful or
OL,17,Feven paranoid about the world around
OL,18,Fthem, they might be hearing voices,
OL,19,Fwhich can steer them away from getting
OL,20,Fthe help they need," Dr Dissanayaka
OL,21,Fadded.
