OL,7,FThe Health Secretary also agreed to
OL,8,Fmeet Jane, who shared her story with
OL,9,FITV News.
OL,11,FHe said: "I would be more than willing
OL,12,Fto meet families who've been victims,
OL,13,Fbut also those families who fear that
OL,14,Fsomeone they love could well become a
OL,15,Fperpetrator of violent crime because
OL,16,Fof their illness."
OL,18,FITV News understands the government
OL,19,Fwill "look carefully" at its planned
OL,20,Freform of the Mental Health Act, in
OL,21,Flight of families' concerns.
