OL,7,FIn a statement, Claire Murdoch, NHS
OL,8,FEngland's National Mental Health
OL,9,FDirector, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,10,Fwith the families and loved ones of
OL,11,FBarnaby Webber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar,
OL,12,Fand Ian Coates, and since the
OL,13,Funacceptable failings in the care
OL,14,Fprovided to Valdo Calocane, the NHS
OL,15,Fhas instructed every local mental
OL,16,Fhealth system to review its policies
OL,17,Fand practices to identify ` and
OL,18,Fprovide appropriate services to `
OL,19,Fthose living with severe mental
OL,20,Fillness who may need intensive and
OL,21,Fassertive community care.
