OL,7,F"This includes reviewing teams
OL,8,Fdelivering dedicated intensive and
OL,9,Fassertive community care as well as
OL,10,Fcore community mental health services,
OL,11,Fand we have provided further guidance
OL,12,Fwhich instructs hospitals not to
OL,13,Fdischarge people if they do not attend
OL,14,Fappointments and reiterates the
OL,15,Fimportance of engaging fully with
